#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Why DDD is Having a Moment"
msgstr "滴滴打车为何风头正劲"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Jeremy opened by noting that DDD seems to be experiencing renewed interest, with multiple presentation requests recently. He theorizes this resurgence relates to the rise of AI-assisted development and agentic systems, where DDD's structured approach to organizing business logic makes it easier for AI tools to understand and generate code."
msgstr "杰里米在开场时指出，DDD 似乎正在重新引起人们的兴趣，最近有多个演讲请求。他认为，这种回潮与人工智能辅助开发和代理系统的兴起有关，DDD 组织业务逻辑的结构化方法使人工智能工具更容易理解和生成代码。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Core Principles of Domain-Driven Design"
msgstr "领域驱动设计的核心原则"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ubiquitous Language"
msgstr "无所不在的语言"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "One of Jeremy's favorite aspects of DDD is the emphasis on **ubiquitous language** - a shared vocabulary between developers and business stakeholders. He illustrated this with the restaurant industry example: \"86 ketchup\" means \"we're out of ketchup\" to anyone who's worked in restaurants, but is completely nonsensical to outsiders."
msgstr "杰里米最喜欢的 DDD 的一个方面是强调无处不在的 *语言* --开发人员和业务利益相关者之间的共享词汇。他以餐饮业为例说明了这一点：对于在餐馆工作过的人来说，\"86 番茄酱 \"的意思是 \"我们没有番茄酱了\"，但对于外人来说，这完全是无稽之谈。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Since every industry has its own language, DDD encourages teams to:"
msgstr "由于每个行业都有自己的语言，因此 DDD 鼓励团队这样做："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Identify and document domain-specific terminology"
msgstr "确定并记录特定领域的术语"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Use that language consistently in code, conversations, and documentation"
msgstr "在代码、对话和文档中始终使用这种语言"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Refine the language iteratively with each sprint or development cycle"
msgstr "在每个冲刺或开发周期中不断改进语言"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Domains and Subdomains"
msgstr "域名和子域"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For the demo, Jeremy built an application for scheduling Quarkus Insights episodes, with several subdomains:"
msgstr "在演示中，杰里米建立了一个用于安排 Quarkus Insights 情节的应用程序，其中包含几个子域："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Programming**: Managing episode content and scheduling"
msgstr "*编程* ：管理剧集内容和时间安排"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**People**: Managing hosts, presenters, and guests"
msgstr "*人员* ：管理主持人、主持人和嘉宾"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Engagement**: Handling viewer interactions and notifications"
msgstr "*参与* ：处理观众互动和通知"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Each subdomain represents a distinct area of business concern with its own models and logic."
msgstr "每个子域代表一个不同的业务关注领域，有自己的模型和逻辑。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Building Blocks of DDD"
msgstr "设计驱动发展（DDD）的基石"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aggregates"
msgstr "骨料"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Aggregates** are the core business concepts that encapsulate business rules (invariants). In Jeremy's example, the `EpisodeAggregate` serves as the root entity:"
msgstr "*聚合* 是封装业务规则（不变式）的核心业务概念。在杰里米的示例中， `EpisodeAggregate` 是根实体："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Key characteristics:"
msgstr "主要特点"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aggregates are **POJOs** with no framework dependencies"
msgstr "聚合是 *POJO* ，不依赖框架"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "All business logic lives in the aggregate"
msgstr "所有业务逻辑都存在于聚合体中"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Aggregates maintain **invariants** (rules that must always be true)"
msgstr "聚合保持 *不变* （规则必须始终为真）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You interact with the object graph through the aggregate root"
msgstr "您可以通过聚合根与对象图交互"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Value Objects"
msgstr "价值对象"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Value objects** encapsulate data with no identity. That is,  a value object is defined entirely by its attributes, not by some unique ID. Examples include addresses, email addresses, or in Jeremy's demo, episode titles:"
msgstr "*值对象* 封装的数据没有标识。也就是说，值对象完全由其属性定义，而不是由某个唯一 ID 定义。例如地址、电子邮件地址，或者杰里米演示中的剧集标题："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Value objects enable validation at creation time and make the domain model more expressive."
msgstr "值对象可以在创建时进行验证，并使领域模型更具表现力。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Domain Events"
msgstr "领域活动"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Domain events** represent facts that the business cares about:"
msgstr "*领域事件* 代表企业关心的事实："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Events are:"
msgstr "活动有"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Statements of fact (they have occurred)"
msgstr "事实陈述（已经发生）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Immutable"
msgstr "不可改变"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Can be replayed"
msgstr "可以重放"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Enable event-driven architecture"
msgstr "启用事件驱动架构"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Unlike **commands** (which can be rejected), events represent things that have already happened."
msgstr "与 *命令* （可以拒绝）不同，事件代表已经发生的事情。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Hexagonal Architecture"
msgstr "六边形建筑"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Layered Approach"
msgstr "分层方法"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Jeremy demonstrated how to structure a DDD application using hexagonal architecture:"
msgstr "杰里米演示了如何使用六边形架构构建 DDD 应用程序："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Infrastructure Layer (Adapters)**:\n"
"- REST endpoints (incoming port)\n"
"- Database repositories (outgoing port)\n"
"- Message brokers (outgoing port)\n"
"- DTOs for wire format"
msgstr "*基础设施层（适配器）* ：- REST 端点（输入端口） - 数据库存储库（输出端口） - 消息代理（输出端口） - 线格式的 DTO"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Application Layer**:\n"
"- Application services that orchestrate business logic\n"
"- Command handlers\n"
"- Domain services for logic that doesn't fit in aggregates"
msgstr "*应用层* ： - 协调业务逻辑的应用服务 - 命令处理程序 - 用于不适合聚合的逻辑的域服务"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**Domain Layer**:\n"
"- Aggregates\n"
"- Value objects\n"
"- Domain events\n"
"- Repository interfaces (not implementations)"
msgstr "*领域层* ： - 聚合 - 值对象 - 领域事件 - 存储库接口（非实现）"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Application Services"
msgstr "应用服务"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Application services orchestrate the workflow:"
msgstr "应用服务协调工作流程："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Separating Concerns"
msgstr "将关注点分开"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A critical aspect of hexagonal architecture is keeping the domain pure:"
msgstr "六边形架构的一个重要方面是保持域的纯净："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Aggregates** have no knowledge of persistence frameworks"
msgstr "*聚合体* 不了解持久性框架"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Repositories** handle the translation between aggregates and entities"
msgstr "*存储库* 处理集合与实体之间的转换"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**Mappers** convert between domain objects and database entities"
msgstr "*映射器* 在域对象和数据库实体之间进行转换"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Trade-offs"
msgstr "权衡利弊"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "More Code, Better Organization"
msgstr "更多代码，更好的组织"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Jeremy was upfront about the main drawback: **you'll write significantly more code** with DDD compared to a simple CRUD application. The demo showed:"
msgstr "杰里米直言不讳地指出了主要缺点：与简单的 CRUD 应用程序相比，使用 DDD *要编写更多的代码* 。演示显示"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Value objects for each domain concept"
msgstr "每个领域概念的价值对象"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Separate DTOs for REST endpoints"
msgstr "针对 REST 端点的独立 DTO"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Commands for operations"
msgstr "操作命令"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Events for notifications"
msgstr "通知事件"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Mappers between layers"
msgstr "层间映射器"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Benefits"
msgstr "好处"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "However, this additional code provides substantial benefits:"
msgstr "然而，这些额外的代码带来了巨大的好处："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**1. Maintainability**: When inheriting code, business logic is easy to find - it's all in the aggregates."
msgstr "*1.可维护性* ：继承代码时，业务逻辑很容易找到--都在聚合体中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**2. Testability**: Aggregates are POJOs that can be tested with plain JUnit, no framework required."
msgstr "*2.可测试性* ：聚合是 POJO，可使用普通 JUnit 进行测试，无需框架。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**3. Flexibility**: Swapping persistence frameworks (e.g., from https://hibernate.org/orm/[Hibernate] to https://firebase.google.com/[Firebase]) only requires changing the repository implementation."
msgstr "*3.灵活性* ：更换持久性框架（如从 link:https://hibernate.org/orm/[Hibernate] 到 link:https://firebase.google.com/[Firebase] ）只需更改存储库的实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**4. Clear boundaries**: Logic doesn't leak across layers or get scattered in event handlers."
msgstr "*4.边界清晰* ：逻辑不会跨层泄漏，也不会分散在事件处理程序中。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "**5. AI-friendly**: The structured approach makes it easier for AI tools to understand and generate code."
msgstr "*5.人工智能友好型* ：结构化方法使人工智能工具更容易理解和生成代码。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Collaboration Between Domains"
msgstr "领域之间的协作"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Jeremy addressed a key question: how do domains interact?"
msgstr "杰里米提出了一个关键问题：各领域如何互动？"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Close Collaboration Pattern"
msgstr "紧密合作模式"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When teams work closely together:"
msgstr "当团队密切合作时："

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Anti-Corruption Layer"
msgstr "反腐败层"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When integrating with external systems you don't control, use an anti-corruption layer to translate between their model and yours, protecting your domain from external changes."
msgstr "在与您无法控制的外部系统集成时，使用防破坏层在他们的模型和您的模型之间进行转换，保护您的领域不受外部变化的影响。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-05-19-quarkus-insights-248-ddd-hexagonal-architecture.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Transaction Boundaries"
msgstr "交易边界"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
